<h1>Chris Sherrod</h1>

<h2><a href="http://christophersherrod.com/now/">christophersherrod.com/now</a></h2>

<h3>“Sharks vs Dolphins in business - <a href="http://christophersherrod.com/business-sharks-vs-dolphins/">http://christophersherrod.com/business-sharks-vs-dolphins/</a>”</h3>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
San Diego
CA
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Entrepreneur and Transformational Publisher at BlissLifePress.com
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I make transformational authors best sellers with a 5000+ email list
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I’m driven to change the world for the better besides making money. That’s why my publishing company focuses on transformational authors where we make them best selling authors with at least a 5000 email list while helping their charity raise funds. We strive for win-win-win in all cases.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
SuperMensch: The Legend Of Shep Gordon - documentary about one of the greatest connectors <a href="http://supermenschthemovie.com">http://supermenschthemovie.com</a>
</p>

